item.description: Welcome to the Bridge Club!!! Bridge is the ultimate partnership card game, where 4 players are dealt a deck of 52 cards equally. The game is complex and strategic, requiring players to bid on the number of tricks they think they can take and then follow suit and play their cards in a specific order. As you can imagine, playing Bridge requires a lot of skill and strategy. It’s a game that rewards careful thought and planning, and even the most experienced players are constantly learning and improving their skills.
